tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE backlink_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    url VARCHAR(255),
    anchor_text VARCHAR(255),
    source_domain VARCHAR(255),
    backlink_status VARCHAR(50),
    backlink_type VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE backlinks (
    backlink_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    anchor_text VARCHAR,
    target_url VARCHAR,
    source_domain VARCHAR,
    backlink_status BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE backlink_analysis (
    analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    backlink_id INT,
    analysis_date DATE,
    analysis_score FLOAT,
    analysis_notes TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE backlinks (
    backlink_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    source_url STRING,
    target_url STRING,
    anchor_text STRING,
    create_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE linked_pages (
    page_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    page_url STRING UNIQUE,
    page_title STRING,
    page_content STRING,
    last_crawled TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE backlink_history (
    history_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    backlink_id UUID REFERENCES backlinks(backlink_id),
    status STRING,
    http_code INT,
    check_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE backlinks (
    backlink_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    url VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    anchor_text VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    domain_authority INT,
    created_at TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE websites (
    website_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    domain VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    created_at TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE pages (
    page_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    url VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    created_at TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE authors (
    author_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    created_at TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE backlink_history (
    history_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    backlink_id INT NOT NULL,
    action VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    created_at TIMESTAMP
)
